<L>__{interior gaming room night}
<A>__{roderick and the chevalier running a faro bank when an important lady suffers a huge loss.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{the ladies were passionately fond of play, and hence would often arise no small trouble to us; for the truth most be told, that the ladies loved to play, but not to pay. the point of honor is not understood by the charming sex; and it was with the greatest difficulty that we could keep them from the table, could get their money if they lost or, if they paid, prevent them from using the most furious and extraordinary means of revenge.}
